  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class HostInfoResponse
extends InfoResponse
    Use this to access host object information as provided in an EPP host info response compliant with RFC5730 and RFC5732. Such a service element is sent by a compliant EPP server in response to a valid host info command, implemented by the HostInfoCommand class.
    See Also:
    HostInfoCommand, Serialized Form
